ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KSHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c736%2c20220630%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSHM,111,聲,736,20220630,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"736","JDATE":"20220630","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}